Enum Class IuReferenceKind

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<IuReferenceKind>
edu.iu.type.IuReferenceKind
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<IuReferenceKind>, Constable
public enum IuReferenceKind extends Enum<IuReferenceKind>
Describes the kind of reference used to refer to a generic type.
